{"id": 2487, "genre": 1000, "title": "【好奇心x贝壳租房】在试图解决“住不好”时，你pick了哪些操作？", "description": "肯定有一招你用过了（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 1407, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180729002416IAOKzBrDChUEnfcs.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-29T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4597, "title": "【好奇心x贝壳租房】在试图解决“住不好”时，你pick了哪些操作？", "content": "肯定有一招你用过了", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 295517, "content": "立即具有“工匠精神”，别说修理了，我就是鲁班本人！", "image": "img/option/option/2018072900245692JAjqCgBaps1uIn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 295518, "content": " 听到隔壁巨大的噪音，我也只能与对方互敲暖气作为回应了。", "image": "img/option/option/20180729002511Q0qw4s7rogkA39dE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 295519, "content": "悄咪咪的安装摄像头，让我看看是谁帮（偷）我（吃）减（零）肥（食）。", "image": "img/option/option/20180729002530jPtVdl2Z9YTQHEkJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 295520, "content": "同事纷纷下班，我却假装加班迟迟不回；那个所谓的房子不过是个睡觉的地方。", "image": "img/option/option/20180729002606KlXR5JyIjYOMa0Hv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 295522, "content": "点一根线香开始安慰自己“佛说要忍耐。”", "image": "img/option/option/20180729002619htpUDHjsECMZQBa7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 295523, "content": "更加努力奋斗，争取提薪升职，让未来的自己住的更好。", "image": "img/option/option/20180729002638enrjWGa70yhfOV9q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 295524, "content": "每日通勤的距离等于一本书的时间，我也是饱览群书的说。", "image": "img/option/option/20180729002651kzSdC1vxZYjANHpW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 295525, "content": "（咣咣凿门声）“X先生，快递” “放门口就行” 一个人住，女生装男生是必备技能。", "image": "img/option/option/20180729002707tSyi7FwMqf9uc0aC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}